Wired2Perform® Calendar enables you to see an overall view across all your calendars. May it be your work, personal or college email calendars. Create calendar events consisting og meeting behavior information and create your own  meeting schedulers according to the event type for people to book meetings with you based on your availability.

Key Features :

1. Discover the unique behavioral styles of your Wired2Perform® meeting participants.

2. Discover the unique behavioral factors of your Wired2Perform® meeting participants

3. Find out the meeting behavior summary of your Wired2Perform® meeting to be more aware:
    • Behavior - the behavior style
    • Communication - the communication style
    • Factor  - the behavior factor
    • Design - the design of the content that you should consider when you communicate with them
    • Information - the information requires that you should consider when you communicate with them
    • Length - the length of the content that you should consider when you communicate with them

4. Find the behavior attributes, behavior talents, and behavior roles of each of your Wired2Perform® meeting participants
